mes New Roman, serif">, </FONT></FONT></SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">нгбанди</FONT></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"> и </FONT></FONT></SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">гбайя</FONT></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">; </FONT></FONT></SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">центральносуданских</FONT></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"> — народы </FONT></FONT></SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">мору-мангбету</FONT></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">. </FONT></FONT></SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">Пигмеи</FONT></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"> говорят на языках своих соседей, то есть всех перечисленных семей, но в основном на языках банту. </FONT></FONT></SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">Сантомийцы</FONT></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"> и </FONT></FONT></SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">аннобонцы</FONT></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FON