rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">Водь</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"> 100 чел. (73 — в </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">России</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111">, </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">перепись</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"> </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">2002 года</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111">) </SPAN> </P> </UL> <P ALIGN=JUSTIFY class="rust134"> <FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif">Волжско-пермская подгруппа</FONT></P> <UL> <LI><P CLASS="western rust161" > <FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">Мордва</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"> 843 350 чел. (в </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">России</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111">, </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">перепись</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"> </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">2002 года</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111">) </SPAN> </P> <UL> <LI><P CLASS="western rust161" > <FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">Мокшане</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"> 300 000 чел. (49 624 чел. — в </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">России</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111">, перепись </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN class="rust110"><FONT COLOR="#000000">2002 года</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN class="rust111"> или до 300 000 чел. по оценке, в том числе в </SPAN><FONT COLOR="#2b5ec7"><SPAN class="rust109"><SPAN